### Create a new rating
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rating
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great service!"
}

### Get all ratings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rating

### Get rating by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rating/1

### Update rating
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rating/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Updated comment"
}

### Delete rating
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rating/1